    "en": {
      "name": "Nerva the Imprisoned Deity of Creation",
      "effect": "3 \"Artmegia\" monsters\nMust first be either Fusion Summoned, or Special Summoned (from your Extra Deck) in Defense Position by Tributing 3 monsters with different Types. You can only Special Summon \"Nerva the Imprisoned Deity of Creation\" once per turn. Cannot be destroyed by card effects while a card is in the Field Zone. Once per turn, when you activate an \"Artmegia\" monster's effect (Quick Effect): You can make the activated effect become \"Destroy all cards your opponent controls\".",
      "official": false
    },
